                <note rend="inline" type="source">723.2515/3235a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Peru</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Moore</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-12-01T16:00:00-05:00"
                            >December 1, 1928—4 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>84. Have you had an interview with President Leguia relating to a settlement of
                    the Tacna-Arica matter along the lines you were talking to me, and with what
                    result? Please make a full report.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
